Calculating NPV


‚Ä¢	 Forecast the cash flows of the project over Its 
economic life 
‚Äì	 Treat investments as negative cash flow 
‚Ä¢	 Determine the appropriate opportunity cost of capital  

(i.e. determine the discount rate r) 
‚Ä¢	 Use opportunity cost of capital to discount the future 
cash flow of the project 
‚Ä¢	 Sum the discounted cash flows to get the net present 
value (NPV) 
