Payback Period


‚Ä¢  How long it takes before entire initial investment is 
recovered through revenue 
‚Ä¢  Insensitive to time value of money, i.e. no discounting

‚Ä¢  Gives equal weight to cash flows before cut-off date & no 
weight to cash flows after cut-off date 
‚Ä¢  Cannot distinguish between projects with different NPV 
‚Ä¢  Difficult to decide on appropriate cut-off date 

