‚Ä¢	 Payback criterion modified to account for the time 
value of money 
‚Äì  Cash flows before cut-off date are discounted

‚Ä¢	 Surmounts objection that equal weight is given to all 
flows before cut-off date 
‚Ä¢	 Cash flows after cut-off date still not given any weight 

