‚Ä¢  A way of including uncertainty and flexibility in the 
program valuation 
‚Ä¢  Key features:

‚Ä¢  Certain aspects of the system may be uncertain, e.g. the  

demand quantity for a given aircraft = UNCERTAINTY

‚Ä¢  In reality, the decision-maker (aircraft manufacturer) has 
the ability to make decisions in real-time according to 
how the uncertainty evolves = FLEXIBILITY 

